                            <comment id="13406409" author="slebresne" created="Wed, 4 Jul 2012 09:58:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch attached to fix. I will note that in practice this was not really a bug because the deletionInfo used were those of the columnIterator, and at that point those deletionInfo should only contain whole row tombstone, not range tombstone. Yet, the code was misleading and could have trigger a bug if the code change underneath.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
